<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .date {
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .address-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .subject {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .signature-img {
            height: 60px;
            margin-bottom: -10px;
        }
        .stamp {
            float: right;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Invitation Letter – Australian Visitor Visa (Subclass 600)</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="date">Date: {{today}}</div>

    <div class="address-section">
        To:<br>
        The Visa Officer<br>
        Department of Home Affairs<br>
        Commonwealth of Australia
    </div>

    <p>Dear Sir/ Madam,</p>

    <div class="subject">Subject: Invitation Letter for Visitor Visa (Subclass 600)</div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>I, <strong>Erwin Pouros</strong>, born on 18 August 1991, currently residing at:</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>Address:</strong><br>
            1–9 Hinkler Drive<br>
            Gold Coast City<br>
            Queensland 4214, Australia<br>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +61 7 5596 1233
        </div>

        <p>I am writing this letter to formally invite <strong>Mr. {{fullName}}</strong>, a {{nationality}} citizen, holder of Passport No. <strong>{{passportNumber}}</strong>, born on {{dob}}, to visit me in Australia under the Visitor Visa (Subclass 600).</p>

        <p>The purpose of his visit is tourism and a short family/friend visit, during which he will stay with me at my above-mentioned residential address in Gold Coast, Queensland. The intended visit is temporary, and he will return to his home country before the expiry of his visa.</p>

        <p><strong>I confirm that:</strong></p>
        <ul style="color: #004a82; font-weight: 500;">
            <li>I am an Australian citizen / permanent resident.</li>
            <li>I will provide accommodation during his stay in Australia.</li>
            <li>The visitor will comply with all Australian visa conditions.</li>
            <li>The visit is purely for tourism and personal visit purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Should you require any further information, please feel free to contact me.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/8Q9Z5bM.png" class="signature-img" alt="Signature">
            <div style="width: 200px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; margin: 10px 0;"></div>
            <p>
                <strong>Erwin Pouros</strong><br>
                Resident Host<br>
                Date: {{today}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
